  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Cyber Tower 2048, you must defend a cybernetic world from insectoids by building defensive fortifications and battling across various locations. Develop your strategy and collect coins from defeated enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic cyber fantasy in the tower defense genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 waves on each unique location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and upgrade defensive structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A system for improving heroes and weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various types of enemies and tactical challenges.</p>",
